{"tid":1170140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"左膠有左膠遊行，勇士有勇士突擊，各有各做，篤灰者連續做二十世冇運行既有病窮撚兼慘死","createTime":"2019-05-24T22:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T06:30:06.000Z","uid":241151,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de3d57ad4d5931a07dca87c5281f824f165c6c66","tid":1170140,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T22:44:48.000Z","msg":"咁就咪又動不動就屈人係乜係物<br />\n<br />\n和理非既你自己行完就返屋企睇你既cctvb，咪阻其他有心人各自既活動，抗爭又唔見你咁好行動力<br />\n<br />\n自己有自己想做既野人，亦無謂同d和理非嘈，各有各做，可向和理非人仕宣傳理念"},{"pid":"aa645b1974e6d3d854b0805d0f7b9ff6b4c87bf5","tid":1170140,"uid":244332,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T22:46:29.000Z","msg":"係，但絕對要提防政府搵黑勢力扮暴徒，同黑警一唱一和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雨革唔係未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c07cdf0f5de9efe1fbc44c3e06eadf9d7c3366b","tid":1170140,"uid":58669,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T22:50:46.000Z","msg":"一定有大量篤灰者<br />\n<br />\n但人地係黎自政黨，你就碌柒"},{"pid":"6dfc26820d5b30f45b7df07c37c79e2f07b0c1ac","tid":1170140,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T23:04:14.000Z","msg":"左膠又黎篤灰啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fb4301089315715a0079572467d6f9f2413c23","tid":1170140,"uid":241151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa645b1974e6d3d854b0805d0f7b9ff6b4c87bf5","tid":1170140,"uid":244332,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T22:46:29.000Z","msg":"係，但絕對要提防政府搵黑勢力扮暴徒，同黑警一唱一和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雨革唔係未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T23:06:16.000Z","msg":"總之遊行既遊行，有新玩法既人就由得佢地去試，唔好亂咁阻止，更加冇理由走去篤人背脊，如果覺得自己可以幫到手，由遊行隊轉去玩新遊戲都可以，倒返轉，如果勇士忽然